20he's%20my%20fan%20because%20I'm%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20his.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20international%20collaborations%20and%20crossovers%2C%20Kareena%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EBuckingham%20Murders%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20a%20small%20kind%20of%20crossover.%20We%20shot%20in%20London%2C%20so%20we%20wanted%20to%20keep%20it%20in%20English%20and%20Hindi%20to%20maintain%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20film%20and%20the%20area%20where%20it%20was%20being%20shot.%20It%20was%20such%20a%20special%20film.%20It's%20going%20to%20come%20on%20Netflix%20on%20November%208.%20I%20somehow%20feel%20being%20a%20first-time%20producer%20on%20the%20film%2C%20it%20was%20something%20extremely%20special.%20I%20think%20it's%20my%20career's%20best%20performance%2C%20so%20I%20want%20people%20to%20watch%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpening%20up%20about%20her%20favourite%20character%20she%20played%20onscreen%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkareena-kapoor-shares-stunning-pics-are-you-team-colour-or-black-and-white-6670035%5C%22%3EKareena%20Kapoor%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20it's%20Geet%20from%20Jab%20We%20Met.%20%26quot%3BShe%20represents%20a%20certain%20punjabiness%20in%20a%20girl%20who%20has%20dreams%2C%20wants%20to%20dream%20big%2C%20follow%20her%20heart%20and%20just%20do%20what%20she%20wants.%20And%2020-25%20years%20later%2C%20it's%20still%20resonating%20in%20a%20pop%20culture%20way.%20That%20is%20one%20reason%20why%20our%20films%20are%20being%20watched%20globally%20and%20are%20enjoyed%20in%20our%20language%20because%20it's%20the%20song%2C%20the%20dance%2C%20and%20they%20wait%20for%20it.%20We%20have%20to%20kind%20of%20be%20true%20to%20our%20heritage%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20everyone%20loves%20about%20it%2C%20and%20that%20is%20also%20what%20sets%20it%20apart.%20We%20have%20so%20many%20different%20kinds%20of%20cinema%E2%80%94whether%20it's%20Korean%2C%20French%2C%20or%20different%20kinds%20of%20international%20cinema%E2%80%94but%20somewhere%20you%20still%20enjoy%20doing%20Naatu%20Naatu%20on%20the%20stage%20of%20the%20Oscars.%20Somewhere%20India%20has%20got%20that%20representation%2C%20and%20it%20feels%20nice%20to%20be%20true%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20professional%20front%2C%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Buckingham%20Murders%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20film%20was%20released%20on%20September%2013%20and%20also%20stars%20Ash%20Tandon%2C%20Ranveer%20Brar%2C%20and%20Keith%20Allen.%20Directed%20by%20Hansal%20Mehta%20and%20written%20by%20Aseem%20Arrora%2C%20Kashyap%20Kapoor%20and%20Raghav%20Raj%20Kakker%2C%20the%20film%20was%20presented%20by%20Balaji%20Telefilms%20and%20produced%20by%20Shobha%20Kapoor%2C%20Ektaa%20R%20Kapoor%2C%20and%20first-time%20producer%20Kareena%20Kapoor.%20Ektaa%20Kapoor%20and%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20have%20previously%20collaborated%20for%20%3Cem%3EVeere%20Di%20Wedding%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ECrew%20%3C%2Fem%3E-%20both%20hits.%20The%20actress%20was%20also%20seen%20in%20%3Cem%3ECrew%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20co-starring%20Kriti%20Sanon%2C%20Tabu%2C%20Diljit%20Dosanjh%20and%20Kapil%20Sharma%20this%20year.%20Before%20that%2C%20she%20starred%20in%20Jaane%20Jaan%20with%20Jaideep%20Ahlawat%20and%20Vijay%20Varma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20personal%20front%2C%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20married%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20in%202012%20and%20the%20star%20couple%20are%20parents%20to%20two%20sons%20-%20Taimur%20and%20Jeh.%20Kareena%20and%20Saif%20have%20co-starred%20in%20films%20like%20T%3Cem%3Eashan%2C%20Omkara%2C%20Kurbaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EAgent%20Vinod%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729591020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fumdhsaog_kareena_625x300_22_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fndtv-world-summit-asked-about-her-favourite-collaboration-kareena-kapoor-picked-no-surprises-there-6846684%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kareena%20Kapoor%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20The%20Buckingham%20Murders%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fndtv-world-summit-asked-about-her-favourite-collaboration-kareena-kapoor-picked-no-surprises-there-6846684%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Analysis%3A%20How%20Hoax%20Bomb%20Threats%20Are%20Damaging%20India's%20Aviation%20Industry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20aviation%20industry%20is%20going%20through%20a%20nightmare%20of%20flight%20disruptions%20after%20a%20series%20of%20bomb%20threats%20that%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20fake.%20The%20government%20has%20launched%20crisis%20management%20efforts%20after%20more%20than%20130%20hoax%20calls%20in%20nine%20days.%20On%20October%2020%2C%20airlines%20in%20India%20received%20as%20many%20as%2024%20bomb%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hoax%20callers%20have%20targeted%20Air%20India%2C%20IndiGo%2C%20Akasa%20Air%2C%20Vistara%2C%20SpiceJet%2C%20Star%20Air%2C%20Alliance%20Air%20and%20even%20international%20flights.%20Some%20threats%20were%20sent%20via%20social%20media%20and%20emails%2C%20others%20were%20found%20written%20in%20lavatories.%20Several%20domestic%20and%20international%20flights%20were%20diverted%20or%20were%20forced%20to%20make%20emergency%20landings%2C%20which%20caused%20panic%20among%20flyers.%20Checks%20by%20bomb%20squads%2C%20causing%20flight%20disruptions%2C%20have%20also%20hit%20airlines%20financially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hoax%20bomb%20calls%20have%20been%20attributed%20to%20factors%20ranging%20from%20malicious%20intent%20and%20attention-seeking%20to%20mental%20health%20issues%2C%20disruption%20of%20business%20operations%20or%20pranking.%20Airlines%20are%20not%20new%20to%20such%20bomb%20hoaxes%2C%20but%20the%20sheer%20frequency%20of%20the%20calls%20this%20time%20is%20astonishing%20and%20debilitating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlying%20hassles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Vistara%20flight%20from%20Frankfurt%20with%20147%20passengers%20and%20crew%20had%20to%20make%20an%20emergency%20landing%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20go%20through%20security%20checks%20in%20an%20isolation%20bay%20after%20a%20bomb%20scare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20an%20Air%20India%20flight%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20New%20York%20had%20to%20be%20diverted%20to%20Delhi%2C%20evacuated%20and%20combed%20for%20any%20bomb.%20The%20plane%20was%20required%20to%20dump%20nearly%20100%20tonnes%20of%20jet%20fuel%20to%20ensure%20a%20safe%20landing%2C%20which%20cost%20the%20airline%20around%20Rs%2010%20million%20-%20a%20huge%20waste.%20It%20was%20reported%20that%20the%20total%20cost%20of%20the%20diversion%2C%20including%20accommodation%20for%20passengers%2C%20grounding%20of%20the%20aircraft%20and%20crew%20replacements%2C%20would%20likely%20exceed%20Rs%2030%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20emergency%20landing%20following%20a%20bomb%20threat%20is%20also%20an%20ordeal%20for%20passengers.%20%26quot%3BEvacuating%20passengers%20at%20the%20earliest%20is%20not%20easy.%20It%20could%20result%20in%20minor%20injuries%20if%20extra%20precaution%20is%20not%20exercised.%20The%20entire%20baggage%20is%20offloaded%20and%20screened.%20It%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Atanu%20Guru%2C%20strategy%20and%20aviation%20expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20harassed%20passengers%20wait%20without%20a%20clue%20of%20what%20turn%20their%20travel%20plan%20might%20take.%20Besides%20being%20time%20consuming%2C%20the%20process%20is%20expensive%20and%20eats%20into%20the%20bottom%20line%20of%20the%20airline.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20it%20might%20affect%20the%20sustainability%20of%20the%20airline%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAuthorities'%20response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlarmed%20by%20the%20fake%20bomb%20threats%2C%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20Security%20(BCAS)%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20CEOs%20and%20representatives%20of%20airlines%20in%20Delhi%20on%20October%2019.%20The%20civil%20aviation%20ministry%20is%20planning%20strict%20rules%20to%20prevent%20such%20incidents.%20For%20one%2C%20those%20behind%20hoax%20calls%20can%20be%20put%20on%20the%20no-fly%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20some%20information%20about%20who%20is%20behind%20the%20hoax%20threats%20and%20the%20BCAS%20is%20looking%20at%20ways%20and%20mechanism%20to%20fix%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20informed%20an%20official%20of%20the%20aviation%20security%20body%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bomb%20threats%20were%20also%20discussed%20in%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Transport%2C%20Tourism%20and%20Culture%2C%20which%20is%20headed%20by%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20MP%20Sanjay%20Jha.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20for%20all%2C%20especially%20the%20passengers%20and%20the%20airlines.%20The%20civil%20aviation%20ministry%20and%20the%20BCAS%20are%20acting%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20report%20and%20the%20action%20taken%20will%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20standing%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20easy%20access%20to%20social%20media%20and%20VPN%20(virtual%20private%20network)%20services%2C%20it%20has%20become%20fairly%20easy%20for%20troublemakers%20to%20send%20out%20anonymous%20bomb%20threats%2C%20while%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20security%20agencies%20to%20track%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20also%20looking%20at%20incorporating%20anti-hoax%20provisions%20that%20are%20in%20operation%20in%20other%20countries.%20Guidelines%20from%20the%20International%20Civil%20Aviation%20Organisation%20(ICAO)%20are%20also%20being%20studied.%20They%20are%20also%20looking%20at%20the%20cybersecurity%20aspect%20of%20the%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20any%20specific%20pattern%20in%20the%20bomb%20threats%2C%20Mr%20Guru%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20where%20the%20threats%20are%20emanating%20from%2C%20they%20are%20targeted%20at%20Indian%20carriers.%20They%20are%20certainly%20not%20one-off%20incidents%20and%20appear%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20mechanisms%20of%20a%20larger%20sinister%20design%20by%20forces%20inimical%20to%20India's%20national%20interests.%20These%20are%20attempts%20at%20maligning%20and%20defaming%20Indian%20brands%2C%20thereby%20trying%20to%20derail%20the%20India%20growth%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20moment%2C%20tracking%20down%20hoaxers%20presents%20a%20challenge%20as%20there%20are%20no%20legal%20provisions%20dealing%20only%20with%20hoax%20bomb%20threats%3B%20they%20are%20treated%20according%20to%20the%20country's%20criminal%20laws.%20There%20are%20SOP%20(standard%20operating%20procedures)%20and%20security%20protocols%2C%20but%20only%20for%20the%20aftermath%20of%20such%20threats.%20There%20is%20not%20much%20in%20existing%20rules%20to%20prevent%20or%20deter%20hoax%20calls%20to%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivil%20Aviation%20Minister%20Ram%20Mohan%20Naidu%20said%20the%20authorities%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20take%20every%20threat%20seriously%2C%20as%20it%20is%20a%20question%20of%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEnhancing%20vigil%2C%20expanding%20intelligence%20networks%20and%20seeking%20international%20cooperation%20would%20certainly%20help%20mitigate%20the%20challenge.%20Sources%20of%20threat%20could%20be%20from%20any%20corner%20of%20the%20world.%20Identifying%2C%20tracking%20and%20apprehending%20the%20offenders%20would%20largely%20depend%20on%20the%20degree%20of%20cooperation%20that%20other%20countries%20are%20willing%20to%20extend%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Guru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20150%20million%20passengers%20flew%20domestically%20in%20India%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20civil%20aviation%20ministry.%20The%20flight%20chaos%20caused%20by%20hoax%20callers%20is%20not%20only%20a%20financial%20strain%20but%20also%20threatens%20to%20have%20an%20adverse%20impact%20on%20the%20tourism%20industry.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729590900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F24r2luh8_runway-generic-plane-generic-airport-generic-unsplash_625x300_01_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-how-hoax-bomb-threats-are-damaging-indias-aviation-industry-6846670%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20aviation%20industry%20is%20going%20through%20a%20nightmare%20of%20flight%20disruptions%20after%20a%20series%20of%20bomb%20threats%20that%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20fake.%20The%20government%20has%20launched%20crisis%20management%20efforts%20after%20more%20than%20130%20hoax%20calls%20in%20nine%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-how-hoax-bomb-threats-are-damaging-indias-aviation-industry-6846670%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tech%20industry's%20%E2%80%98Shah%20Jahan%E2%80%99%20throws%20party%20for%20disco%20queen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729590628000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114460026%2Cimgsize-76638.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Fsocial%2Ftech-industrys-shah-jahan-throws-party-for-disco-queen%2Farticleshow%2F114459640.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20hosted%20a%2070s-themed%20disco%20party%20for%20his%20wife%2C%20Priscilla%20Chan.%20Clad%20in%20sparkling%20outfits%2C%20the%20couple%20celebrated%20with%20a%20lively%20crowd.%20Zuckerberg%20humorously%20interacted%20with%20followers%2C%20sharing%20insights%20about%20their%20relationship%20and%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Shah%20Jahan%E2%80%99%20throws%20party%20for%20disco%20qu