n%20that%20something%20more%20than%20an%20incremental%20adjustment%20was%20warranted%2C%26quot%3B%20Belski%20said%20in%20the%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20encouraged%20by%20the%20broadening%20out%20of%20the%20stock%20market%20rally%2C%20as%20it's%20no%20longer%20concentrated%20in%20a%20handful%20of%20tech%20giants.%20That's%20healthy%20behavior%20for%20sustainable%20stock%20market%20gains%2C%20according%20to%20the%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20trend%20we%20expect%20to%20continue%20and%20should%20help%20to%20support%20future%20market%20gains%20even%20if%20the%20price%20and%20fundamental%20performance%20of%20Mag-X%20stocks%20continues%20to%20decelerate%20in%20the%20months%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20Belski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fc7c3d7b-c8d5-4665-bd3c-1c08a92b6ce4%5C%22%3EThe%20Bears%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bearish%20strategists%20on%20Wall%20Street%20are%20sticking%20to%20their%20views%20even%20after%20being%20wrong%20all%20year.%20Their%20top%20worry%20is%20the%20potential%20for%20fewer%20interest%20rate%20cuts%20than%20expected%20and%20growing%20hype%20in%20AI%20that%20might%20fail%20to%20deliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20strategists%20have%20held%20firm%20to%20their%20bearish%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20year-end%20price%20target%20of%204%2C200%2C%20which%20represents%20potential%20downside%20of%2028%25%20from%20current%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20JPMorgan%20strategist%20Dubravko%20Lakos-Bujas%20admitted%20that%20a%20recession%20appears%20off%20the%20table%20but%20said%20that%20AI%20investments%20are%20unlikely%20to%20pay%20off%20with%20lingering%20questions%20around%20monetization%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20investor%20expectations%20of%20a%20Federal%20Reserve%20that%20is%20about%20to%20embark%20on%20a%20string%20of%20interest%20rate%20cuts%20could%20be%20disappointed%20if%20the%20economy%20continues%20to%20stay%20resilient%2C%20as%20it%20would%20limit%20the%20Fed's%