0during%20the%20BRICS%20Business%20Forum%20in%20Moscow%20on%20Friday.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FAlexander%20Zemlianichenko%2C%20Pool%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERussia%20is%20hosting%20a%20BRICS%20summit%20this%20week%2C%20showing%20the%20limits%20of%20attempts%20to%20isolate%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20grouping%20is%20buoyant%20after%20ballooning%20from%20five%20members%20to%20nine.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20larger%20membership%2C%20though%2C%20widens%20the%20chance%20of%20internal%20conflict%20that%20impedes%20the%20bloc's%20aims.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20flexing%20its%20muscles%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20BRICS%20economic%20bloc%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20rival%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nation%20is%20hosting%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20group%20this%20week%2C%20the%20first%20since%20the%20group%20almost%20doubled%20its%20membership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20larger%20grouping%20gives%20members%20more%20weight%20%E2%80%94%20and%20is%20a%20rebuke%20to%20Western-led%20attempts%20to%20isolate%20Russia%20economically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20also%20complicates%20things%2C%20introducing%20new%20competing%20interests%20and%20rivalries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeopolitical%20analysts%20say%20it%20could%20dilute%20the%20group's%20ability%20to%20take%20action%20and%20reduce%20it%20to%20a%20talking%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran%2C%20Egypt%2C%20Ethiopia%2C%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20are%20the%20new%20BRICS%20entrants%2C%20joining%20the%20earlier%20members%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20China%2C%20Brazil%2C%20and%20South%20Africa.%20Saudi%20Arabia%20has%20been%20invited%20to%20join%20but%20has%20not%20formally%20done%20so%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20touted%20the%20expansion%20as%20proof%20of%20the%20group's%20%26quot%3Bgrowing%20authority%26quot%3B%20and%20role%20in%20international%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20geopolitical%20tensions%20and%20competing%20interests%20within%20the%20group%20are%20dragging%20down%20Russia's%20efforts%20to%20use%20it%20to%20chip%20away%20at%20the%20dominance%20of%20the%20West%2C%20particularly%20the%20US%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBRICS%20expansion%20is%20no%20easy%20task%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Abishur%20Prakash%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20The%20Geopolitical%20Business%2C%20a%20strategy%20advisory%20firm%20in%20Toronto.%20%26quot%3BIt%20risks%20creating%20rival%20camps%20within%20the%20group.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a422f5a1-a2fa-40bb-898f-89b58f30e598%5C%22%3EA%20'raw'%20grouping%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20bloc's%20founding%20in%202006%20%E2%80%94%20with%20Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20and%20China%20as%20members%20before%20South%20Africa%20joined%20in%202010%20%E2%80%94%20it%20has%20tried%20to%20challenge%20Western%20economic%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20its%20members%20experienced%20significant%C2%A0economic%20growth.%20After%20the%20recent%20expansion%2C%20its%20member%20states%20represent%20almost%C2%A046%25%20of%20the%20world's%20population%20and%20about%C2%A025%25%20of%20global%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20more%20than%2040%20countries%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrics-summit-countries-interested-brazil-russia-india-china-south-africa-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpressed%20interest%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20joining%20the%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Anton%20Barbashin%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20editorial%20director%20at%20Riddle%20Russia%2C%20an%20online%20journal%20on%20Russian%20affairs%2C%20described%20the%20group%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Braw%20collection%26quot%3B%20of%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20chance%26quot%3B%20of%20political%20unity%20given%20its%20members'%20competing%20interests%20and%20starkly%20differing%20attitudes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20have%20grappled%20with%20internal%20disagreements%20over%20relations%20with%20the%20West%2C%20territorial%20claims%2C%20and%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20are%20engaged%20in%20internal%20standoffs.%20India%20and%20China%20have%20clashed%20over%20disputed%20territory%20along%20their%20border%2C%20though%20they%20announced%20a%20deal%20on%20patrolling%20arrangements%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20countries%20%E2%80%94%20notably%20India%20and%20South%20Africa%20%E2%80%94%20also%20have%20a%20tricky%20balancing%20act%20to%20do%2C%20engaging%20with%20the%20group%20without%20alienating%20their%20partners%20in%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221875563d-1228-4de5-a7cc-5b63106239c1%5C%22%3ETalking%20shop%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBarbashin%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20was%20important%20for%20Russia%20because%20it%20had%20been%20cut%20out%20from%20other%20international%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20way%20to%20communicate%20and%20possibly%20strike%20%26quot%3Bsome%20deals%20in%20the%20future%20that%20we%20don't%20necessarily%20foresee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20representatives%20of%2032%20countries%20are%20set%20to%20attend%20the%20summit%20this%20week%2C%20according%20to%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Barbashin%20said%20the%20group's%20size%20masked%20its%20relative%20impotence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20a%20nice%20facade%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20it%20falls%20within%20the%20idea%20that%20economic%20growth%20should%20translate%20into%20a%20greater%20political%20setting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeaders%20are%20expected%20to%20discuss%20how%20far%20members%20are%20willing%20to%20commit%20to%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUna%20Aleksandra%20Berzina-Cerenkova%2C%20the%20director%20at%20Riga%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EStradins%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUniversity's%20China%20Studies%20Center%2C%20told%20Politico%20that%20%26quot%3BChina%20uses%20BRICS%20to%20give%20it%20a%20mandate%20to%20push%20global%20visions%20and%20post-Weste