wers%2C%20and%20I've%20noticed%20multiple%20subtleties%20that%20indicate%20AI%20was%20used.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-ai-is-a-tool-not-a-creature-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20can%20be%20a%20powerful%20tool%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20improving%20efficiency%20and%20formatting%2C%20but%20AI-written%20answers%20often%20sound%20generic%20and%20structurally%20look%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20that%2C%20using%20AI%20can%20also%20strip%20an%20application%20of%20personality%20and%20diminish%20an%20applicant's%20ability%20to%20set%20themself%20apart%20among%20potentially%20thousands%20of%20other%20applicants.%20Here's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-job-listing-catches-ai-applications-with-prompt-injection-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20spot%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20how%20it%20can%20impact%20the%20decision%20to%20hire%20an%20applicant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2289566fd1-d898-4b73-b6e4-3ee71a0c42ab%5C%22%3ESmall%20details%20can%20show%20that%20an%20applicant%20has%20used%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20noticed%20many%20candidates%20are%20now%20trying%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproject-theia-amazon-ai-tool-shopping-inspiration-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20for%20inspiration%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20still%20writing%20their%20test%20answers%20themselves.%20In%20those%20cases%2C%20it's%20unlikely%20I%2C%20or%20any%20other%20person%2C%20could%20spot%20the%20usage%20of%20AI%20when%20looking%20at%20a%20piece%20of%20text%20in%20isolation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20of%20any%20AI%20models%20that%20can%20decipher%20human%20versus%20AI-generated%20content%20with%20100%25%20accuracy.%20In%20fact%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farstechnica.com%2Finformation-technology%2F2023%2F07%2Fwhy-ai-detectors-think-the-us-constitution-was-written-by-ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20large%20AI%20models%20falsely%20classifying%20things%20like%20the%20Bible%20and%20the%20US%20Constitution%20as%20AI-generated.%20This%20leaves%20us%20in%20a%20very%20cloudy%20atmosphere%20with%20no%20foolproof%20way%20of%20deciphering%20whether%20AI%20was%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20at%20Applied%2C%20we've%20begun%20utilizing%20a%20similarity%20detector.%20In%20this%20method%2C%20a%20human%20from%20our%20team%20compares%20several%20answers%20to%20the%20same%20question%20and%20flags%20any%20recurring%20similarities%20between%20syntax%2C%20paragraph%20structure%2C%20and%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20found%20it%20much%20easier%20to%20see%20patterns%20emerging%20when%20examining%2020%20to%2030%20applications%20simultaneously%20rather%20than%20just%20looking%20at%20one%20in%20isolation.%20After%20doing%20countless%20rounds%20of%20similarity%20detecting%2C%20we've%20found%20that%20it's%20often%20small%20details%2C%20like%20formatting%20and%20punctuation%2C%20that%20giveaway%20an%20applicant's%20usage%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e35e63b5-e396-4c7f-8c15-755cdbb3b47f%5C%22%3EDead%20giveaways%20AI%20was%20used%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20found%20that%20text%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20AI-generated%20if%20every%20word%20in%20a%20sentence%20is%20capitalized%20or%20if%20there%20are%20unnecessary%20capital%20letters%20in%20phrases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI-written%20text%20also%20tends%20to%20generate%20extra%20punctuation%20that%20doesn't%20read%20in%20the%20way%20people%20speak.%20I've%20also%20noticed%2C%20when%20examining%20multiple%20applications%20for%20a%20specific%20role%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20AI-assisted%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20have%20the%20exact%20same%20number%20of%20headings%2C%20paragraphs%2C%20and%20bullets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e72bf10e-67a3-4e94-8246-5dad2cfcbb4e%5C%22%3ESometimes%20using%20AI%20to%20complete%20an%20application%20isn't%20a%20big%20deal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20give%20power%20to%20the%20human%20reviewer%20to%20decide%20whether%20each%20application%20is%20worth%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployers-can-tell-use-chatgpt-ai-job-application-cover-letter-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflagging%20for%20AI%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20even%20then%2C%20we%20won't%20automatically%20reject%20someone%20if%20one%20person%20believes%20AI%20was%20used.%20It's%20a%20lot%20more%20nuanced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20in%20the%20power%20of%20the%20crowd%2C%20so%20if%20someone%20flags%20a%20skills-test%20answer%2C%20we'll%20have%20other%20team%20members%20review%20it%20and%20come%20to%20a%20collective%20decision%20that%20considers%20the%20candidate's%20entire%20application%20and%20skillset.%20We%20allow%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20control%20and%20debate%20within%20each%20hiring%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20mention%20that%20many%20organizations%20operate%20in%20different%20ways.%20They%20may%20not%20mind%20the%20use%20of%20AI%2C%20or%20they%20might%20discard%20an%20applicant%20entirely%20if%20there%20is%20even%20suspicion%20that%20AI%20was%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220ab82a56-3466-4e9e-ba6a-5c976e8ce059%5C%22%3EAI%20isn't%20going%20anywhere%2C%20so%20use%20it%20to%20your%20advantage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20that%20AI%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20used%20in%20applications.%20I've%20had%20conversations%20with%20several%20people%20on%20the%20job%20hunt%20who've%20told%20me%20they%20use%20AI%20to%20even%20out%20the%20power%20dynamic%20between%20themselves%20and%20employers%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20use%20AI%20in%20their%20own%20hiring%20processes.%20I%20think%20that's%20fair.%20But%2C%20if%20you're%20going%20to%20use%20it%2C%20use%20it%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-models-microsoft-openai-meta-google-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELarge%20language%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20GPT%20are%20great%20at%20synthesizing%20information%2C%20writing%20concisely%2C%20and%20creating%20structure%2C%20which%20can%20be%20incredibly%20useful%20for%20candidates%20whose%20native%20language%20isn't%20English%20or%20who%20aren't%20fluent.%20People%20applying%20to%20software%20engineer%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffailed-meta-coding-test-technical-interview-tips-regrets-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20science%20roles%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20be%20asked%20to%20use%20AI%20during%20practical%20tests.%20In%20these%20cases%2C%20don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20put%20your%20digital%20skills%20on%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20rather%20than%20use%20AI%20to%20complete%20job%20applications%2C%20I%20advise%20candidates%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20help%20identify%20the%20key%20skills%20and%20attributes%20that%20hiring%20managers%20will%20be%20looking%20for.%20Run%20the%20job%20description%20through%20ChatGPT%2C%20and%20ask%20it%20to%20summarise%20and%20share%20examples%20of%20relevant%20skills%20and%20how%20they%20might%20be%20used%20in%20practice.%20This%20valuable%20information%20can%20then%20be%20used%20to%20inform%20your%20own%20responses%20to%20application%20and%20interview%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you're%20an%20employer%20who%20would%20like%20to%20share%20your%20experience%20with%20AI%20in%20the%20hiring%20process%2C%20email%20Tess%20Martinelli%20at%20tmartinelli%40businessinsider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-employers-know-ai-used-job-application-resume-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729588303000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670e75603f2165d716e0cda7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-employers-know-ai-used-job-application-resume-2024-10%22%2C%22summa