wrence%20Bishnoi%20%26quot%3BEncounter%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Kshatriya%20Karni%20Sena%20has%20offered%20a%20cash%20reward%20of%20Rs%201%2C11%2C11%2C111%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bencounter%26quot%3B%20of%20jailed%20gangster%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Flawrence-bishnoi%5C%22%3ELawrence%20Bishnoi%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20cash-for-murder%20reward%2C%20declared%20by%20Raj%20Shekhawat%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Kshatriya%20Karni%20Sena%2C%20is%20to%20avenge%20the%20death%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Flawrence-bishnoi%5C%22%3ESukhdev%20Singh%20Gogamedi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20prominent%20Rajput%20leader%20who%20was%20gunned%20down%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20in%20December%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Raj%20Shekhawat%20can%20be%20seen%20offering%20a%20reward%20to%20any%20police%20officer%20who%20kills%20the%20jailed%20gangster.%20Bishnoi%20is%20currently%20lodged%20in%20Gujarat's%20Sabarmati%20jail%20under%20charges%20related%20to%20cross-border%20drug%20smuggling.%20Recently%2C%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20minister%20Baba%20Siddique%20and%20has%20been%20linked%20to%20a%20firing%20incident%20outside%20Bollywood%20actor%20Salman%20Khan's%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%20last%20year%2C%20Mr%20Gogamedi%20was%20gunned%20down%20in%20broad%20daylight%2C%20while%20sipping%20tea%20at%20his%20Jaipur%20home.%20Two%20of%20the%20men%20he%20was%20sitting%20with%20opened%20fire%2C%20killing%20him%20and%20leaving%20his%20security%20guard%20critically%20injured.%20One%20of%20the%20shooters%2C%20Naveen%20Singh%20Shekhawat%2C%20was%20also%20killed%20during%20the%20exchange%20of%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20attack%2C%20Rohit%20Godara%2C%20a%20known%20associate%20of%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20and%20Goldie%20Brar%20gangs%2C%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20Mr%20Gogamedi's%20murder.%20Godara%20posted%20on%20social%20media%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20Rohit%20Godara%20Kapursari%2C%20brother%20of%20Goldie%20Brar.%20Today%20we%20take%20full%20responsibility%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20Sukhdev%20Gogamedi.%20He%20used%20to%20back%20our%20enemies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20sparked%20massive%20protests%20across%20Rajasthan%2C%20with%20Rajput%20groups%20demanding%20justice%20for%20their%20murdered%20leader.%20The%20assassination%20of%20Mr%20Gogamedi%2C%20a%20figure%20closely%20associated%20with%20the%20Rajput%20community%20and%20Karni%20Sena%2C%20ignited%20public%20outrage%2C%20particularly%20as%20it%20coincided%20with%20a%20political%20transition%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20had%20just%20ousted%20the%20Congress-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20video%20message%2C%20Raj%20Shekhawat%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLawrence%20Bishnoi%20is%20the%20killer%20of%20our%20precious%20gem%20and%20heritage%20Amar%20Shaheed%20Sukhdev%20Singh%20Gogamedi%20ji.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Gogamedi's%20murder%2C%20Rajasthan%20police%20arrested%20Ashok%20Meghwal%2C%20a%20key%20suspect%2C%20and%20eight%20others.%20A%20multi-state%20investigation%2C%20led%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%2C%20resulted%20in%20raids%20across%2031%20locations%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Haryana.%20The%20NIA%20teams%20seized%20a%20large%20cache%20of%20pistols%2C%20ammunition%2C%20mobile%20phones%2C%20SIM%20cards%2C%20digital%20video%20recorders%20(DVRs)%2C%20and%20financial%20documents%20during%20the%20raids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20Mr%20Gogamedi's%20assassination%2C%20Rohit%20Godara%2C%20has%20not%20been%20traced.%20According%20to%20intelligence%20reports%2C%20Godara%20fled%20India%20using%20a%20fake%20passport%20under%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BPawan%20Kumar.%26quot%3B%20Interpol%20has%20issued%20a%20Red%20Notice%20for%20Godara%20who%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20hiding%20somewhere%20in%20Canada.%20With%20over%2032%20criminal%20cases%20registered%20against%20him%2C%20including%20extortion%20and%20murder%2C%20Godara%20is%20one%20of%20India's%20most-wanted%20criminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729586280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fju407kqo_lawrence-bishnoi_625x300_22_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flawrence-bishnoi-rs-1-11-11-111-karni-senas-cash-offer-for-lawrence-bishnoi-encounter-6846084%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Kshatriya%20Karni%20Sena%20has%20offered%20a%20cash%20reward%20of%20Rs%201%2C11%2C11%2C111%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bencounter%26quot%3B%20of%20jailed%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flawrence-bishnoi-rs-1-11-11-111-karni-senas-cash-offer-for-lawrence-bishnoi-encounter-6846084%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nasa%20alert!%20580-feet%20asteroid%20set%20to%20pass%20by%20Earth%20on%20October%2024%2C%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729586100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114456332%2Cimgsize-49972.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fscience%2Fnasa-alert-580-feet-asteroid-set-to-pass-by-earth-on-october-24-2024%2Farticleshow%2F114456280.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NASA%20confirms%20asteroid%20363305%20(2002%20NV16)%2C%20about%20580%20feet%20wide%2C%20will%20pass%20Earth%20safely%20on%20October%2024%2C%202024%2C%20at%204.52%20million%20kilometres%20away.%20Though%20labelled%20as%20potentially%20hazardous%2C%20there's%20no%20danger.%20NASA%20continuously%20monitors%20such%20threats%2C%20demonstrating%20preparedness%20with%20missions%20like%20the%20DART%20to%20ensure%20Earth's%20safety%20from%20future%20asteroid%20