d%20batter%20met%20the%20fate%20as%20he%20was%20serving%20as%20the%20replacement%20of%20Ajinkya%20Rahane%20in%20Chennai%20and%20the%20return%20of%20the%20latter%20saw%20Nair%20getting%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20stating%20that%20such%20a%20theory%20would%20also%20see%20Sarfaraz%20getting%20dropped%2C%20Chopra%20said%20the%20team%20management%20will%20continue%20with%20the%20batter%20in%20the%20playing%20XI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20theory.%20Karun%20Nair%20made%20300%2C%20but%20was%20dropped%20in%20the%20next%20match.%20Why%3F%20Because%20he%20was%20playing%20in%20place%20of%20Ajinkya%20Rahane%20in%20that%20match%2C%20and%20with%20the%20latter%20coming%20back%2C%20Nair%20fell%20back%20in%20pecking%20order.%20A%20Test%20career%20that%20could%20have%20been%2C%20might%20have%20been...Nair%20never%20got%20that%20continuity.%20Going%20by%20that%20theory%2C%20Sarfaraz%20will%20sit%20out%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20that%20won't%20happen.%20One%20more%20thing%20is%20important%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20-%20outside%20noise%20-%20and%20that%20favours%20Sarfaraz%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Chopra%20said%20on%20JioCinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729582740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fadt9asd8_sarfaraz-khan-bcci_625x300_21_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-new-zealand-2024%2Fsarfaraz-khan-will-sit-out-but-bcci-sent-triple-centurion-reminder-on-india-xi-for-2nd-test-6839433%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20suffered%20an%20embarrassing%20eight-wicket%20loss%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20New%20Zealand%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20of%20the%20three-match%20series%20at%20M%20Chinnaswamy%20Stadium%2C%20Bengaluru.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-new-zealand-2024%2Fsarfaraz-khan-will-sit-out-but-bcci-sent-triple-centurion-reminder-on-india-xi-for-2nd-test-6839433%22%2C%2