ar%20Pradesh's%20Bahraich%20after%20a%20communal%20clash%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20indirectly%20warned%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%20against%20any%20bulldozer%20action.%20The%20court%20said%20it%20is%20the%20state%20government's%20%26quot%3Bchoice%26quot%3B%20if%20it%20wants%20to%20risk%20violating%20the%20top%20court's%20directions.%20The%20court%2C%20however%2C%20noted%20that%20its%20orders%20in%20the%20'bulldozer%20justice'%20case%20specify%20that%20it%20will%20not%20intervene%20if%20the%20structures%20facing%20demolition%20are%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20Justice%20KV%20Viswanathan%20has%20asked%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20not%20to%20take%20any%20action%20before%20the%20next%20hearing%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20the%20petitioners%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20CU%20Singh%20told%20the%20bench%20that%20local%20authorities%20issued%20demolition%20notices%20after%20the%20October%2013%20violence%20--%20which%20claimed%20one%20life%20--%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20respond%20within%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApplicant%20No.1's%20father%20and%20brothers%20surrendered...%20notices%20purportedly%20issued%20on%2017%20Oct%2C%20but%20pasted%20on%2018th%20evening...%20we%20sought%20hearing%20on%20Sunday%2C%20but%20that%20did%20not%20happen.%20Some%20have%20approached%20HC%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20extended%20to%2015%20days%20the%20deadline%20to%20file%20replies%20to%20the%20demolition%20notices%20and%20directed%20the%20state%20authorities%20to%20decide%20after%20considering%20the%20responses.%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20KM%20Nataraj%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%2C%20assured%20the%20court%20that%20no%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20till%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20(UP%20authorities)%20want%20to%20take%20the%20risk%20of%20flouting%20our%20order%2C%20it's%20their%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Gavai%20said%20today.%20Justice%20Viswanathan%20added%20that%20the%20high%20court%20had%20given%2015%20days%20to%20file%20replies%20to%20the%20demolition%20notices.%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20petitioners%20have%20not%20been%20granted%20any%20protection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20currently%20hearing%20a%20bunch%20of%20petitions%20against%20'bulldozer%20justice'%20-%20a%20term%20used%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20practice%20of%20razing%20the%20property%20of%20individuals%20accused%20in%20criminal%20cases.%20The%20trend%20has%20caught%20on%20in%20several%20states%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20among%20them.%20The%20court%20has%20clarified%20that%20being%20accused%20of%20a%20crime%20cannot%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20the%20demolition%20of%20property%20and%20only%20violation%20of%20civic%20rules%20may%20attract%20such%20action.%20The%20court%20has%20also%20paused%20demolitions%20carried%20out%20without%20its%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Happened%20In%20Bahraich%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2013%2C%20an%20altercation%20broke%20out%20in%20Bahraich's%20Maharajganj%20when%20a%20group%20of%20people%20objected%20to%20loud%20music%20near%20a%20mosque%20during%20a%20procession%20for%20Durga%20Puja%20idol%20immersion.%20This%20snowballed%20into%20arson%20and%20vandalism%20in%20the%20area%2C%20forcing%20the%20local%20administration%20to%20snap%20Internet%20connectivity.%20Ram%20Gopal%20Mishra%2C%2022%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20during%20the%20clash.%20A%20video%20that%20circulated%20after%20the%20clash%20showed%20Mishra%20removing%20a%20green%20flag%20from%20a%20rooftop%20and%20replacing%20it%20with%20a%20saffron%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20arrested%20five%20persons%20suspected%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20Mishra's%20death%20--%20Mohammad%20Faheen%2C%20Mohammad%20Sarfaraz%2C%20Abdul%20Hameed%2C%20Mohammad%20Taleem%20alias%20Sabloo%2C%20and%20Mohammad%20Afzal.%20Mohammad%20Talim%20and%20Mohammad%20Sarfaraz%20were%20arrested%20after%20they%20suffered%20gunshots%20in%20an%20encounter%20with%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20police.%20Police%20said%20the%20accused%20were%20trying%20to%20cross%20into%20Nepal%20when%20they%20were%20caught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20104%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20violence%20and%2023%20establishments%20have%20been%20served%20demolition%20notices.%20Among%20those%20who%20were%20served%20notices%20is%20Hameed%2C%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20killing.%C2%A0Authorities%2C%20however%2C%20claim%20the%20notices%20were%20issued%20as%20part%20of%20a%20routine%20anti-encroachment%20drive.%20The%20notices%20have%20sparked%20panic%20among%20local%20residents%20as%20shopkeepers%20were%20seen%20vacating%20their%20premises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729580700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fch7ohea8_supreme-court-bulldozer-split_625x300_22_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-bulldozer-uttar-pradesh-bahraich-if-they-want-to-risk-supreme-courts-bulldozer-action-warning-to-up-6845415%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hearing%20a%20challenge%20to%20demolition%20notices%20served%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Bahraich%20after%20a%20communal%20clash%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20indirectly%20warned%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%20against%20any%20bulldozer%20action.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-bulldozer-uttar-pradesh-bahraich-if-they-want-to-risk-supreme-courts-bulldozer-action-warning-to-up-6845415%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Is%20Al-Qard%20Al-Hassan%2C%20Hezbollah's%20Main%20Cash%20Source%20Targeted%20By%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael%20recently%20targeted%20branches%20of%20Al-Qard%20Al-Hassan%20(AQAH)%2C%20a%20financial%20institution%20linked%20to%20the%20Iran-backed%20Lebanese%20militant%20group%20Hezbollah%2C%20with%20precision%20airstrikes.%20The%20strikes%20hit%20across%20Beirut's%20southern%20suburbs%2C%20southern%20Lebanon%2C%20and%20the%20northeastern%20Beqaa%20Valley%2C%20areas%20known%20as%20Hezbollah%20strongholds.%20These%20attacks%2C%20which%20spanned%20late%20Sunday%20night%20into%20Monday%20morning%2C%20are%20part%20of%20Israel's%20effort%20to%20cripple%20Hezbollah's%20financial%20infrastructure%20and%20weaken%20its%20ability%20to%20fund%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20confirmed%20that%20at%20least%2011%20branches%20of%20AQAH%20were%20struck%2C%20in%20a%20campaign%20aimed%20at%20dismantling%20Hezbollah's%20access%20to%20vital%20financial%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Al-Qard%20Al-Hassan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%201983%2C%20Al-Qard%20Al-Hassan%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20%26quot%3Bthe%20benevolent%20loan%2C%26quot%3B%20calls%20itself%20a%20charitable%20organisation%20adhering%20to%20Islamic%20finance%20principles%2C%20which%20prohibit%20interest.%20Its%20mission%20is%20to%20provide%20interest-free%20loans%20to%20Lebanon's%20Shiite%20population%2C%20particularly%20those%20aligned%20with%20Hezbollah.%20AQAH%20offers%20loans%20against%20collateral%20such%20as%20gold%20or%20jewellery%2C%20offering%20much-needed%20credit%20to%20a%20Lebanese%20population%20battling%20a%20declining%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hezbollah-hamas-israel-claims-it-found-500-million-in-secret-hezbollah-bunker-in-beirut-6843741%5C%22%3EIsrael%20Claims%20It%20Found%20%24500%20Million%20In%20%26quot%3BSecret%26quot%3B%20Hezbollah%20Bunker%20In%20Beirut%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl-Qard%20Al-Hassan%20allegedly%20operates%2030%20branches%20across%20Lebanon%2C%20with%20many%20located%20in%20Hezbollah-controlled%20areas%20of%20Beirut.%20Its%20influence%20surged%20after%20Lebanon's%20financial%20collapse%20in%202019%2C%20as%20traditional%20banks%20severely%20limited%20depositors'%20access%20to%20their%20savings.%20AQAH%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20continued%20to%20operate%2C%20allowing%20those%20who%20banked%20with%20it%20to%20withdraw%20cash%20-%20often%20in%20hard%20currency%20-%20when%20other%20financial%20institutions%20could%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAQAH%20operates%20under%20a%20license%20granted%20by%20the%20Lebanese%20government.%20The%20US%20Department%20of%20the%20Treasury%20sanctioned%20AQAH%20in%202007%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20serving%20as%20Hezbollah's%20financial%20arm.%20US%20officials%20contend%20that%20while%20AQAH%20may%20serve%20Lebanon's%20Shiite%20population%2C%20it%20is%20also%20used%20to%20move%20Hezbollah's%20funds%20through%20shell%20accounts%2C%20allowing%20the%20group%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20the%20international%20financial%20system%2C%20despite%20sanctions%20designed%20to%20cut%20off%20its%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHezbollah's%20Use%20Of%20AQAH%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%2C%20which%20emerged%20as%20a%20dominant%20force%20in%20Lebanon%20after%20Israel's%201982%20invasion%20of%20the%20country%2C%20has%20long%20relied%20on%20hawala%20networks%20and%20financial%20mechanisms%20to%20build%20and%20maintain%20support%2C%20especially%20among%20Lebanon's%20Shiite%20population.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20Al-Qard%20Al-Hassan%20has%20become%20a%20crucial%20element%20in%20Hezbollah's%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Lebanon%2C%20there%20are%20hawala%20systems%20that%20work%20as%20money-exchange%20houses%20and%20move%20large%20quantities%20of%20sums.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20Lebanese%20citizens%2C%20particularly%20Hezbollah's%20constituency%2C%20depend%20on%20AQAH%20for%20hard%20currency%20loans%2C%20with%20collateral%20as%20simple%20as%20jewellery%20or%20gold.%20While%20the%20average%20loan%20does%20not%20exceed%20%245%2C000%2C%20these%20loans%20are%20essential%20lifelines%20for%20those%20trying%20to%20pay%20for%20weddings%2C%20education%2C%20or%20starting%20small%20businesses.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20Hezbollah%20has%20extended%20the%20invitation%20for%20all%20Lebanese%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20sect%20or%20political%20affiliation%2C%20to%20utilize%20AQAH's%20services.%20The%20group%20has%20promoted%20AQAH%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20traditional%20banking%20system%2C%20which%20collapsed%20amidst%20the%202019%20economic%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah's%20leadership%20has%20been%20open%20about%20the%20group's%20dependence%20on%20AQAH%20for%20financial%20support.%20After%20the%20organisation%20was%20hacked%20in%202020%20and%20the%20names%20of%20its%20clients%20were%20leaked%2C%20Hezbollah's%20former%20leader%2C%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%2C%20publicly%20defended%20AQAH.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-kills-hezbollah-finance-chief-in-syria-managed-main-source-of-income-6843838%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BManaged%20Main%20Source%20Of%20Income%26quot%3B%3A%20Israel%20Kills%20Hezbollah%20Finance%20Chief%20In%20Syria%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20confirmed%20that%20one%20of%20the%20strikes%20targeted%20a%20vault%20underneath%20a%20hospital%20building%20in%20Beirut%2C%20which%20they%20claim%20held%20%24550%20million%20meant%20to%20fund%20Hezbollah's%20military%20activities.%20These%20financial%20resources%2C%20Israel%20argues%2C%20are%20essential%20for%20Hezbollah%20to%20continue%20purchasing%20weapons%20and%20paying%20fighters.%20Israeli%20defence%20officials%20have%20alleged%20that%20AQAH%20is%20responsible%20for%20safeguarding%20as%20much%20as%20%24750%20million%20a%20year%20in%20Iranian%20funding%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20rev