software%20engineer%20at%20Deloitte.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhenever%20she%20visits%20home%2C%20Rani%20prepares%20her%20favourite%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337560%2Fkathalfy-founder-aman-chhabra-brings-jackfruit-ready-to-eat-product-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejackfruit%20chips%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20Ana%20proudly%20shares%20with%20her%20colleagues%20in%20Bengaluru.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20follows%20a%20unique%20way%20of%20drying%20the%20jackfruits.%20Then%2C%20she%20cools%20them%20down%20and%20refries%20them.%20I%20have%20never%20tasted%20chips%20like%20hers%20anywhere%20else.%20That%E2%80%99s%20something%20I%20really%20miss%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ana%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20society%20where%20women%20are%20often%20underestimated%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20running%20soaring%20businesses%2C%20Rani%20stands%20as%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20resilience%20and%20entrepreneurial%20excellence.%20Her%20journey%20from%20a%20homemaker%20to%20a%20successful%20entrepreneur%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20power%20of%20determination%2C%20hard%20work%2C%20and%20creativity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20hope%20my%20story%20serves%20as%20an%20inspiration%20to%20aspiring%20entrepreneurs%20and%20demonstrates%20that%20with%20vision%20and%20perseverance%2C%20one%20can%20turn%20challenges%20into%20opportunities%20and%20achieve%20remarkable%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20remarks%20Rani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora.%20All%20photos%3A%20Ana.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729516979000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmighty-millets-13-1729261129.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D371250%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kerala-based%20Rani%20Sunny%20transformed%20jackfruit%20into%20innovative%20products%20like%20dried%20jackfruit%2C%20seed%20powder%2C%20and%20