%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Feducation-for-childen-in-tribal-areas-of-Odisha-2-1728999446-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Feducation-for-childen-in-tribal-areas-of-Odisha-2-1728999446-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-370350%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20ThinkCenters%20are%20places%20where%20children%20from%20Odisha%20villages%20are%20encouraged%20to%20attend%20classes%20and%20learn%20from%20the%20volunteers%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20young%20generation%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20worries%20are%20about%20the%20next%20promotion%20or%20appraisal.%20My%20father%20drew%20a%20humble%20salary%20but%20yet%20gave%20to%20charity.%20I%20found%20that%20life%20is%20bigger%20than%20a%20corporate%20package.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDas%E2%80%99%20learnings%20are%20many-pronged%2C%20fertilising%20the%20off-shoots%20of%20Ek%20Asha%E2%80%99s%20endeavours.%20One%20of%20the%20four%20arms%20of%20the%20Trust%20is%20the%20Online%20Thinking%20Class%20(OTC)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20bridge%20that%20connects%20Classes%206%20to%2010%20students%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F255198%2Fodisha-women-tribal-system-kodarapalli-thengapalli-forest-protection-environment-natural-resources-over-exploitation-guard-conservation-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribal%20belts%20of%20Odisha%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20volunteer%20teachers%20from%20across%20the%20globe%20who%20have%20mastery%20in%20a%20certain%20discipline.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20doctors%20teaching%20biology%2C%20engineers%20taking%20STEM%20classes%2C%20geo-scientists%20teaching%20geography%2C%20mathematicians%20teaching%20Vedic%20Math%2C%20and%20artists%20teaching%20crafts%2C%E2%80%9D%20Das%20elaborates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E